draw strength from the unique talents and abilities inherent in a diverse workforce and we believe that the best and most innovative products come from an inclusive workplace where varied viewpoints are welcomed and encouraged if you require accommodation due to a disability in order to complete the application process please review our process for requesting accommodations eeo policy statement eeo is the law top interventional cardiologist medical device products  boston scientific choose your country or region usa australianz brazil china deutschland europe india japan korea malaysia united states need help contact us health care professionals interventional cardiology interventional cardiology products interventional cardiology products a a resize print interventional cardiology products our broad suite of pci solutions makes us the clear partner when treating patients with heart disease view all coronary products  coronary product catalog featured products watchman™ left atrial appendage closure device synergy™ everolimuseluting platinum chromium coronary stent system crossboss™ coronary cto crossing catheter peripheral vascular products innovative solutions for treating vascular system blockages in areas such as the carotid and renal arteries and the lower extremities view all peripheral vascular products  peripheral vascular product catalog featured products jetstream™atherectomy system angiojet™ thrombectomy system epic™ vascular selfexpanding stent system top customer support  boston scientific choose your country or region usa australianz brazil china deutschland europe india japan korea malaysia united states healthcare professionals support cardiac rhythm and latitude™ support  cardiac   availability email us spinal cord stimulation support   mondayfriday am  pm eastern email us all other products   mondayfriday am  pm eastern email us ordering  returns ordering options returns gs  gtin standards online ordering latitude nxt online ordering eorder all oth