ic type public traded as nyse bsx sp  component industry medical device founded  founders john abele founder  director emeritus peter nicholas founder  director emeritus headquarters marlborough massachusetts united states key people michael mahoney president chairman and ceo daniel brennan cfo revenue   billion  operating income   million  net income   million  number of employees  december  website wwwbostonscientificcom boston scientific corporation boston scientific is a worldwide developer manufacturer and marketer of medical devices whose products are used in a range of interventional medical specialties including interventional radiology interventional cardiology peripheral interventions neuromodulation neurovascular intervention electrophysiology cardiac surgery vascular surgery endoscopy oncology urology and gynecology boston scientific is primarily known for the development of the taxus stent a drugeluting stent which is used to open clogged arteries with the full acquisition of cameron health in june  the company also became notable for offering a minimally invasive implantable cardioverterdefibrillator icd which they call the emblem subcutaneous implantable defibrillator sicd contents  history  lawsuits  johnson  johnson lawsuits  restatement  profits  notes  external links historyedit boston scientific was formed june   as a holding company for a medical products company called meditech and to position the company for growth in interventional medicine the company went public through an ipo on may   the taxus stent was approved in  in europe and other countries and approved in the united states by the fda in march  it was the second drugeluting stent approved in the united states on april   the company acquired longtime competitor guidant for  billion the former guidant was split between bsc and abbott laboratories navilyst medical was formed in february  from boston scientifics fluid management and vascular access business units in october  the company was fined  by the us department of justice for paying a us army doctor to use their devices and recommend them to others companies portal in june  boston scientific officially acquired cameron health for a total sum of  billion paid out incrementally as various revenue milestones were achieved in march  the company announced it would acquire endo international plcs urology business for at least  billion expanding the companys health and prostate treatments lawsuitsedit johnson  johnson lawsuitsedit beginning in  boston scientific and johnson  johnson were involved in a series of litigations involving patents covering heart stent medical devices both parties claimed that the other had infringed upon their patents the litigation was settled once boston scientific agreed to pay  million to johnson  johnson in september  and an additional  billion in february  it was announced in november  that johnson  johnson would have another chance for payback after a multibillion dollar trial was set for  november  a new york federal court judge would hear the case without a jury to decide whether boston scientific should be held liable for the contract breach restatementedit on nov  boston scientific restated its financial results for  as well as its quarterly results for the first three quarters of  due to the occurrence of business irregularities in the operations of its japanese subsidiary profitsedit profits rose to € million in  in the irishbased plant in  the profits were € million profits increased by  in one year notesedit  httpwwwbostonheraldcombusinessbusinessmarketsceomahoneytobechairmanofbostonscientific  a b c d boston scientific  annual report pdf   a b shelley wood  mar  fda approves taxus paclitaxeleluting stent wwwmedscapecom retrieved  feb    a b boston scientific closes cameron health acquisition pr newswire ubm plc  june  retrieved  february    emblem sicd system boston scientific archived from the original on  february  retrieved  february    a b about us  hi